<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ru">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Платёж не прошёл | Горностайл72</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/kuliga.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.2/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    :root {
      --kuliga-primary: #1e90ff;
      --kuliga-primary-dark: #0f5db6;
      --kuliga-red: #e74c3c;
      --kuliga-red-dark: #c0392b;
      --kuliga-white: #ffffff;
      --kuliga-gray-100: #f2f5f9;
      --kuliga-gray-200: #e2e8f0;
      --kuliga-gray-500: #64748b;
      --kuliga-gray-700: #334155;
    }

    * {
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }

    body {
      font-family: 'Inter', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, 'Helvetica Neue', Arial, sans-serif;
      background: var(--kuliga-gray-100);
      color: var(--kuliga-gray-700);
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 24px;
    }

    .payment-modal {
      background: var(--kuliga-white);
      max-width: 540px;
      width: 100%;
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 24px 64px rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.15);
      padding: 0;
      overflow: hidden;
      position: relative;
      border: 2px solid rgba(231, 76, 60, 0.1);
    }

    .payment-modal__header {
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--kuliga-red) 0%, var(--kuliga-red-dark) 100%);
      padding: 32px 28px;
      text-align: center;
      color: var(--kuliga-white);
      position: relative;
    }

    .payment-modal__icon {
      width: 80px;
      height: 80px;
      margin: 0 auto 20px;
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      font-size: 40px;
      animation: shake 0.5s ease-out;
    }

    @keyframes shake {
      0%, 100% { transform: translateX(0); }
      25% { transform: translateX(-10px); }
      75% { transform: translateX(10px); }
    }

    .payment-modal__title {
      font-size: 28px;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin: 0;
      line-height: 1.2;
    }

    .payment-modal__body {
      padding: 32px 28px;
    }

    .payment-message {
      background: #fef2f2;
      border-left: 4px solid var(--kuliga-red);
      padding: 16px;
      border-radius: 8px;
      margin-bottom: 24px;
      font-size: 15px;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: var(--kuliga-gray-700);
    }

    .payment-message__text {
      margin: 0;
    }

    .payment-modal__actions {
      display: flex;
      flex-direction: column;
      gap: 12px;
    }

    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      gap: 8px;
      padding: 14px 24px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 16px;
      text-decoration: none;
      transition: all 0.2s ease;
      border: none;
      cursor: pointer;
      width: 100%;
    }

    .btn-primary {
      background: var(--kuliga-primary);
      color: var(--kuliga-white);
      box-shadow: 0 8px 24px rgba(30, 144, 255, 0.25);
    }

    .btn-primary:hover {
      background: var(--kuliga-primary-dark);
      transform: translateY(-2px);
      box-shadow: 0 12px 32px rgba(30, 144, 255, 0.35);
    }

    .btn-secondary {
      background: #fee2e2;
      color: var(--kuliga-red);
      border: 2px solid #fecaca;
    }

    .btn-secondary:hover {
      background: #fecaca;
      transform: translateY(-1px);
    }

    @media (max-width: 600px) {
      body {
        padding: 16px;
      }

      .payment-modal {
        border-radius: 16px;
      }

      .payment-modal__header {
        padding: 24px 20px;
      }

      .payment-modal__icon {
        width: 64px;
        height: 64px;
        font-size: 32px;
      }

      .payment-modal__title {
        font-size: 24px;
      }

      .payment-modal__body {
        padding: 24px 20px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="payment-modal">
    <div class="payment-modal__header">
      <div class="payment-modal__icon">
        <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
      </div>
      <h1 class="payment-modal__title">Платёж не прошёл</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="payment-modal__body">
      <div class="payment-message">
        <p class="payment-message__text">
          Возможно, на карте не хватает нужной суммы или ошибка в реквизитах. Попробуйте заплатить другой картой. Если не получится — свяжитесь с продавцом.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="payment-modal__actions">
        <button onclick="window.close()" class="btn btn-primary">
          <i class="fas fa-times"></i>
          Закрыть
        </button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>

